<section xmlns   ="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"
         xmlns:xl="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"
         xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"
         xml:id  ="mds-content-update"
         xml:lang="en"
         version ="5.0">
  <title>Update selected contents</title>
  <para>
    You can update selected contents of a document in the repository from an XML file.
  </para>
  <warning>
    <para>
      Be careful with this operation.
    </para>
    <para>
      It is possible to corrupt or lose the document if the file used is not well formed.
    </para>
  </warning>
  <para>
    To update selected contents of a document in the repository from an XML file:
  </para>
  <orderedlist>
    <listitem>
      <para>
        Right-click in the browser that includes the contents to update at a certain document node and select <emphasis role="strong">Update...</emphasis>.
      </para>
      <para>
        <mediaobject>
          <alt>select</alt>
          <imageobject>
            <imagedata scalefit="1" width="100%" contentdepth="100%" fileref="src/site/extension/images/en/ide/extension/manage/mds/801.png" format="PNG"/>
          </imageobject>
        </mediaobject>
      </para>
      <para/>
    </listitem>
    <listitem>
      <para>
        In the <emphasis role="strong">Update Resource</emphasis> choose the XML file that you would like to use update the content of the Metadata Service document you selected in step 1.
      </para>
      <para>
        <mediaobject>
          <alt>select</alt>
          <imageobject>
            <imagedata scalefit="1" width="100%" contentdepth="100%" fileref="src/site/extension/images/en/ide/extension/manage/mds/802.png" format="PNG"/>
          </imageobject>
        </mediaobject>
      </para>
      <para>
        Click <emphasis role="strong">Open</emphasis> to transfer the content from the XML file of your choice to the Metadata Service Repository in the selected document.
      </para>
      <para/>
     <para/>
    </listitem>
    <listitem>
      <para>
        You will be notified about the success of the task.
      </para>
      <para>
        <mediaobject>
          <alt>select</alt>
          <imageobject>
            <imagedata scalefit="1" width="100%" contentdepth="100%" fileref="src/site/extension/images/en/ide/extension/manage/mds/803.png" format="PNG"/>
          </imageobject>
        </mediaobject>
      </para>
      <para/>
    </listitem>
    <listitem>
      <para>
        Open the modified file inside of JDeveloper to verify the content of the modified document.
      </para>
    </listitem>
  </orderedlist>
</section>